---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: How Fresh Coat Painters Increased Close Rate by 52% | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/contractors-trades/painters" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Painters
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Article Header -->
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900/30 text-green-700 dark:text-green-300 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Case Study</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">7 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
          How Fresh Coat Painters Increased Close Rate by 52%
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          A Vaughan painting contractor stopped losing jobs to slow response and built a review reputation that commands premium prices.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
          <span>February 2026</span>
          <span class="mx-3">•</span>
          <span>Lead Flow North Team</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <!-- Results Banner -->
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Results at a Glance</h2>
            <p class="text-indigo-100">After 10 months with Lead Flow North</p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">52%</div>
              <div class="text-indigo-100">Higher Close Rate</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">2.8x</div>
              <div class="text-indigo-100">More Estimates</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">156</div>
              <div class="text-indigo-100">Google Reviews</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">18%</div>
              <div class="text-indigo-100">Higher Prices</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Article Content -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

          <!-- Client Overview -->
          <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-6 rounded-xl my-8 not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Client Overview</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Business:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Fresh Coat Painters</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Location:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Vaughan, Ontario</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Type:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Residential interior/exterior</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Team Size:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Owner + 6 painters</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>

          <p>
            Marco Ricci started Fresh Coat Painters in 2018 with one truck and a commitment to quality. His work spoke for itself, but getting in front of homeowners was a constant battle.
          </p>

          <p>
            "I was losing jobs to painters I knew weren't as good," Marco explains. "They just answered the phone faster. I'd be rolling out a ceiling, miss three calls, and by the time I called back, they'd scheduled someone else already."
          </p>

          <p>The numbers were frustrating:</p>

          <ul>
            <li><strong>Average response time:</strong> 3-5 hours</li>
            <li><strong>Estimate follow-up:</strong> Sporadic at best</li>
            <li><strong>Close rate:</strong> 28% of estimates</li>
            <li><strong>Google reviews:</strong> 31 (4.6 stars)</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Solution</h2>

          <p>We implemented a complete lead and reputation system:</p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Instant Lead Response</h3>

          <p>
            Every lead now gets an immediate automated response with photos of recent work, a brief intro, and easy estimate scheduling. Marco reviews responses between jobs and follows up with qualified leads.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Estimate Follow-Up Automation</h3>

          <p>
            After providing an estimate, automated follow-ups go out on a proven schedule. Each message is personalized to the project type and includes a simple way to ask questions or accept.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. Review Generation System</h3>

          <p>
            After every completed job, clients receive an automated review request during peak satisfaction—right after the final reveal. Before/after photos make it easy for clients to share.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Results</h2>

          <div class="overflow-x-auto my-8">
            <table class="min-w-full">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b-2 border-slate-300">
                  <th class="text-left py-3 pr-4">Metric</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4">Before</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4">After</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 pl-4">Change</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr class="border-b">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Response Time</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">3-5 hours</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">Instant + 1hr personal</td>
                  <td class="py-3 pl-4 text-green-600 font-semibold">-85%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Close Rate</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">28%</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">43%</td>
                  <td class="py-3 pl-4 text-green-600 font-semibold">+52%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Google Reviews</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">31</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">156</td>
                  <td class="py-3 pl-4 text-green-600 font-semibold">+403%</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b">
                  <td class="py-3 pr-4">Average Job Size</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">$2,100</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4">$2,480</td>
                  <td class="py-3 pl-4 text-green-600 font-semibold">+18%</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-indigo-500 pl-6 my-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-4">
              "I went from chasing leads to having leads chase me. My 156 reviews mean I don't have to be the cheapest anymore—clients trust me before I even show up for the estimate."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 not-italic">— Marco Ricci, Owner</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <!-- CTA Box -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-purple-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Fill Your Schedule?</h3>
            <p class="text-indigo-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see how we can implement similar results for your painting business.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-indigo-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
